{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-chenfeng-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-chenfeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "poem", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·陳風·009.1", "text_original": "胡為乎株林？從夏南。匪適株林，從夏南。\n駕我乘馬，說于株野。乘我乘駒，朝食于株。", "text_normalized": "胡為乎株林？從夏南。匪適株林，從夏南。\n駕我乘馬，說于株野。乘我乘駒，朝食于株。", "notes": "株林 Chinese poem 1."}
